data.description: Nestled within the serene embrace of countryside tranquility, this impeccably maintained 1,500 square-foot home offers an idyllic retreat on a sprawling 1.6-acre lot. As you approach, the first thing you'll notice is the picturesque setting, with no neighbors to the rear, granting you unobstructed views of nature's bounty. You'll enjoy the freedom to savor the natural beauty of the surroundings, creating a sanctuary of serenity that is both modern and timeless. Welcome to your new haven of comfort and style.
